## Summary

**Root cause**: The marketing-head agent failed because the Claude API usage quota was exhausted. Both swarm runs (`21-16-13` and `21-24-11`) and all 3 fix cycles hit the same single-line error:

```
You're out of extra usage · resets 12am (Australia/Sydney)
```

**This is not a code bug.** No files need editing, no tests need fixing. The agent never got to execute — it was rejected at the API level before any work began.

**Resolution**: Re-run the marketing-head agent after the usage quota resets (12:00 AM AEST). The fix report has been written to `.claude/team-state/fix-marketing-head-status.md`.
